---
title: Taco-Style Turkey Bowls with Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour, this dish gives you the fiesta without the fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair perfectly with tender turkey for a tasty taco bowl that comes together with our smoky Mexican seasoning.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-style-taco-a-la-dinde-553ecca5.jpg
